#Create dummy variables in order to encode categorical, yes/no data points into 1/0 numerical values.
md_df['D.Gender'] = [1 if v == 'Male' else 0 for v in md_df['Gender']]
md_df['D.ReAdmis'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['ReAdmis']]
md_df['D.Soft_drink'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Soft_drink']]
md_df['D.HighBlood'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['HighBlood']]
md_df['D.Stroke'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Stroke']]
md_df['D.Overweight'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Overweight']]
md_df['D.Arthritis'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Arthritis']]
md_df['D.Diabetes'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Diabetes']]
md_df['D.Hyperlipidemia'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Hyperlipidemia']]
md_df['D.BackPain'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['BackPain']]
md_df['D.Anxiety'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Anxiety']]
md_df['D.Allergic_rhinitis'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Allergic_rhinitis']]
md_df['D.Reflux_esophagitis'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Reflux_esophagitis']]
md_df['D.Asthma'] = [1 if v == 'Yes' else 0 for v in md_df['Asthma']]

# Drop original categorical features from dataframe
md_df = md_df.drop(columns=['Gender','ReAdmis','Soft_drink','HighBlood','Stroke','Overweight','Arthritis','Diabetes',

        'TotalCharge', 'Timely_admission','Initial_days',
       'Timely_treatment', 'Timely_visits', 'Reliability', 'Options',
       'Treatment_hours', 'Courteous_staff', 'Active_Listening', 'D.Gender',
       'D.ReAdmis', 'D.Soft_drink', 'D.HighBlood', 'D.Stroke', 'D.Overweight',
       'D.Arthritis', 'D.Diabetes', 'D.Hyperlipidemia', 'D.BackPain',
       'D.Anxiety', 'D.Allergic_rhinitis', 'D.Reflux_esophagitis', 'D.Asthma']]).fit()
print(lm_Initialdays.summary())
